w%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Trinamool%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20source%20added%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20%26quot%3Bwas%20very%20patient%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20seat-sharing%20negotiations.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20gracious%20enough.%20But%20all%20we%20saw%20was%20delay%2C%20delay%20and%20delay%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20remarks%20that%20sent%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20back%20to%20the%20drawing%20board%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20yesterday%20announced%20that%20Trinamool%20would%20fight%20solo%20in%20Bengal%20and%20take%20a%20decision%20on%20any%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%20only%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20since%20been%20in%20damage%20control%20mode%2C%20assuring%20the%20strained%20ties%20would%20be%20mended.%20Senior%20party%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20has%20said%20they%20will%20find%20a%20%26quot%3Bsolution%20to%20the%20impasse%26quot%3B.%20Mr%20Ramesh%20had%20yesterday%20said%20the%20Congress%20%26quot%3Bcannot%20imagine%20INDIA%20bloc%20without%20Mamataji%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20whose%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20entered%20Bengal%20today%2C%20said%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20will%20fight%20injustice.%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20am%20happy%20to%20have%20come%20to%20West%20Bengal.%20We%20have%20come%20here%20to%20listen%20to%20you%20and%20stand%20with%20you.%20BJP-RSS%20are%20spreading%20hatred%2C%20violence%20and%20injustice.%20So%2C%20INDIA%20formation%20is%20going%20to%20fight%20anyay%20(injustice)%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee's%20remarks%20on%20the%20alliance%20had%20come%20after%20talks%20on%20sharing%20seats%20hit%20a%20roadblock.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20was%20offering%20two%20seats%20to%20the%20Congress%20in%20Bengal%2C%20but%20the%20latter%20wanted%20at%20least%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMatters%20reached%20a%20tipping%20point%20when%20Mr%20Chowdh