Widow%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20belief%20that%20getting%20wed%20this%20year%20brings%20bad%20luck.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20debating%20whether%20the%20government%20should%20warn%20against%20against%20superstitions%20that%20say%202024%20is%20a%20bad%20year%20to%20marry%2C%20as%20the%20country%20frets%20over%20its%20declining%20and%20aging%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20folk%20rumors%20that%20this%20year%20is%20the%20'Year%20of%20the%20Widow'%20and%20is%20not%20suitable%20for%20marriage%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20letter%20to%20China's%20Ministry%20of%20Civil%20Affairs%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F5993531560%2FNDlxp52QO%3Frefer_flag%3D1001030103_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewent%20viral%20on%20Chinese%20social%20media%20on%20Wednesday%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThis%20seriously%20deviates%20from%20common%20and%20scientific%20sense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20clear%20who%20sent%20the%20message%20on%20January%2011%20through%20the%20ministry's%20forum%2C%20which%20takes%20open%20questions%20from%20citizens.%20They%20asked%20Beijing%20to%20issue%20a%20public%20notice%20advising%20people%20against%20allowing%20superstition%20to%20affect%20their%20life%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20officials%20appear%20to%20be%20listening.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20giving%20attention%20to%20the%20suggestion%20you%20raised%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ministry%20wrote%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20response%20has%20ignited%20conversation%20about%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20folk%20belief%2C%20with%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fs.weibo.com%2Fweibo%3Fq%3D%2523%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%259B%259E%25E5%25A4%258D%25E9%25BE%2599%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25AE%259C%25E7%25BB%2593%25E5%25A9%259A%2523%26Refer%3Dweibo_weibo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E300%20million%20views%20on%20the%20topic%20on%20Weibo%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20China's%20version%20of%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe