n.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-really-happens-to-the-human-body-during-plane-turbulence-4928696%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-really-happens-to-the-human-body-during-plane-turbulence-4928696%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22One%20Dose%20of%20HPV%20Vaccine%20Helps%20Prevent%20Cervical%20Cancer%3A%20Indian%20Study%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25121330%2Fdiana-polekhina-ZBstHWt9vLc-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EEven%20though%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1995855%5C%22%3Edismissed%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20single-dose%20human%3Cbr%3E%5Cnpapillomavirus%20(HPV)%20vaccination%20against%20cervical%20cancer%20would%20be%20included%20in%20the%20routine%20immunisation%20programme%2C%20a%20new%20study%20conducted%20at%20hospitals%20across%20India%20has%20pointed%20out%20that%20one%20dose%20of%20the%20vaccine%20can%20prevent%20the%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHPV%20is%20a%20sexually-transmitted%20infection%20that%20is%20responsible%20for%20almost%20all%20cases%20of%20cervical%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20was%20conducted%20on%202%2C135%20women%20over%2010%20years%2C%20divided%20into%20groups%20who%20received%20one%2C%20two%20or%20three%3Cbr%3E%5Cndoses%20of%20HPV%20vaccines%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2010%20and%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20study%2C%20conducted%20at%20hospitals%20across%20India%2C%20found%20that%2010%20years%20after%20vaccination%2C%20a%20high%20proportion%20of%20single-%20dose%20recipients%20still%20had%20antibody%20titers%20against%20HPV%20types%2016%20and%2018%20with%20the%20proportion%20being%20slightly%20higher%20among%2010-14-year-olds%20than%20those%20aged%2015-18%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fsingledose-hpv-jab-is-enough-to-prevent-cervical-cancer-indian-study-finds-11706118127728.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELivemint%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%2C%20quoting%20the%20study%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20%3Cem%3EHuman%20Vaccines%20and%20Immunotherapeutics%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20this%20year%2C%20there%20were%20reports%20in%20the%20media%20saying%20that%20the%20HPV%20vaccine%20was%20to%20be%20included%20in%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20vaccine%20programme%2C%20targeting%20girls%20aged%209-14.%20However%2C%20the%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%20has%20since%20clarified%20that%20no%20such%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%20yet.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Union%20Health%20Ministry%20is%20yet%20to%20take%20a%20decision%20on%20the%20roll%20out%20of%20HPV%20vaccination%20in%20the%20country.%20It%20is%20closely%20monitoring%20the%20incidences%20of%20cervical%20cancer%20cases%20in%20the%20country%20and%20is%20in%20regular%20touch%20with%20states%20and%20various%20health%20departments%20regarding%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20PIB%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20research%2C%20%3Cem%3ELivemint%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%2C%20was%20carried%20out%20%E2%80%9Cto%20study%20the%20long-term%20antibody%20response%20after%20a%20single%20dose%20of%20the%20HPV%20vaccine%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20study%20showed%20that%20a%20single%20dose%20jab%20with%20a%20catch-up%20extended%20to%20age%2020%20will%20have%20more%20significant%20impact%20in%20reducing%20the%20lifetime%20risk%20of%20cervical%20cancer%20and%20accelerating%20elimination%20of%20the%20disease%20than%20administering%20two%20doses%20to%20pre-adolescent%20girls.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECervical%20cancer%20is%20the%20second%20most%20prevalent%20form%20of%20cancer%20among%20Indian%20women%2C%20after%20breast%20cancer.%20Across%20the%20world%2C%20the%20HPV%20vaccine%20has%20been%20recognised%20as%20an%20important%20preventive%20measure.%20The%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20has%20recommended%20that%20girls%20aged%20between%209%20and%2014%20should%20be%20given%20one%20or%20two%20HPV%20doses.%20A%20recent%20study%20in%20Scotland%20found%20that%20there%20were%20no%20cases%20of%20cervical%20cancer%20among%20women%20who%20received%20the%20full%20HPV%20immunisation%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc19132k8ke0o%5C%22%3EBBC%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706165052000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F25121330%2Fdiana-polekhina-ZBstHWt9vLc-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fone-dose-of-hpv-vaccine-helps-prevent-cervical-cancer-indian-study%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20government%20has%20denied%20reports%20that%20the%20HPV%20vaccine%20has%20been%20made%20a%20part%20of%20the%20government's%20routine%20immunisation%20programme.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fone-dose-of-hpv-vaccine-helps-prevent-cervical-cancer-indian-study%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Look%20Into%20My%20Eyes%E2%80%99%20Review%3A%20Psychics%20Shed%20the%20Mystique%20In%20a%20Funny%2C%20Compassionate%20Doc%20Portrait%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706164920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fbqlibpn89LookIntoMyEyes-Still1.jpeg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235886893%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CLook%20Into%20My%20Eyes%E2%80%9D%20opens%20with%20an%20unexpectedly%20sobering%2C%20even%20provocative%20encounter%20for%20a%20documentary%20about%20New%20York%20City%20psychics%20and%20their%20clientele%3A%20not%20a%20fanciful%20palm%20reading%20or%20a%20conjuring%20of%20a%20lost%20loved%20one%2C%20but%20an%20attempt%20to%20reckon%20with%20long-festering%20professional%20trauma.%20A%20middle-aged%20female%20doctor%2C%20sharply%20dressed%2C%20talks%20directly%20to%20camera%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guy%20Lodge%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Freviews%2Flook-into-my-eyes-review-1235886893%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Freviews%2Flook-into-my-eyes-review-1235886893%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Freviews%2Flook-into-my-eyes-review-1235886893%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Podcaster%20Praises%20India's%20Policies%2C%20Says%20Country%20%26quot%3BNot%20Afraid%20Of%20China%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20China%20are%20often%20seen%20as%20rivals%2C%20with%20both%20competing%20for%20strategic%20dominance%20in%20the%20realms%20of%20trade%2C%20development%2C%20and%20investment.%20Recently%2C%20Patrick%20Bet%20David%2C%20an%20American%20author%20and%20entrepreneur%2C%20drew%20a%20comparison%20between%20India%20and%20China%2C%20focusing%20on%20both%20the%20nations'%20foreign%20and%20development%20policies.%20He%20asserted%20that%20''India%20is%20not%20afraid%20of%20China''%20and%20also%20hailed%20India%20for%20standing%20up%20to%C2%A0its%20Asian%20neighbour.%20A%20short%20clip%20of%20the%20US%20author's%20podcast%20has%20gone%20viral%20after%20industrialist%20Harsh%20Goenka%20shared%20it%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20Mr%20David%20says%2C%20''iPhones%20are%20now%20being%20made%20in%20India.%20First%20time%20not%20been%20made%20in%20China.%20It%20says%2C%20%E2%80%98made%20in%20India'.%20Guess%20who%20blocked%20TikTok%20in%20their%20country%20%E2%80%93%20India.%20Who%20blocked%20100%20apps%20in%20China%3F%20India.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr.%20Goebka%20simply%20captioned%20the%20video%20as%2C%20''India%20vs%20China''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%20the%20video%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22es%5C%22%3EIndia%20vs%20China%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FKv5U8fRekt%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FKv5U8fRekt%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Harsh%20Goenka%20(%40hvgoenka)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhvgoenka%2Fstatus%2F1749416739224666534%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr.%20David%20further%20praised%20India%20saying%20how%20the%20country%20learned%20from%20China's%20mistakes%20and%20noted%20the%20latter's%20policy%20failures%20like%20the%20'one-child%20policy'%20and%20'overexpansion.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''But%20India%20has%20also%20seen%20the%20mistakes%20China%20made%20with%20the%20one-child%20rule%20and%20over-expansion.%20The%20average%20age%20of%20a%20Chinese%20right%20now%20is%2038.4%20years%20old.%20India%20is%2027%2F28.%20India's%20IIT%20Institute%20is%20producing%20incredible%20engineers.%20Many%20companies%20here%20will%20hire%20Indian%20engineers%20and%20they%20are%20rockstars.%20Better%20than%20MIT%20in%20many%20cases.%20So%2C%20I%20think%20India%20is%20very%20important%20for%20the%20next%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%20years.%20As%20long%20as%20India%20is%20there%2C%20China's%20going%20to%20hate%20it%2C%20they're%20not%20going%20to%20like%20it%2C''%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20has%20sparked%20debate%20online%2C%20with%20the%20video%20receiving%20varied%20responses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20wrote%2C%20''India%20is%20the%20future%20of%20this%20planet.%20Without%20India%20world%20has%20no%20existence.%20Our%20holistic%20legacy%20is%20remarkable%2C%20none%20can%20match%20it.%20Our%20youth%20power%20has%20tremendous%20potential%2C%20if%20utilised%20brilliantly%20then%20nothing%20is%20impossible%20for%20us.%20Hope%20India%20will%20emerge%20unique%20as%20always.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20said%2C%20''India%20has%20great%20potential%2C%20even%20China%20knows%20that%20we%20need%20to%20improve%20our%20manufacturing%20and%20transport%20facilities%20like%20fast%20approvals%20and%20increase%20freight%20speed.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20added%2C%20''Thank%20you%20Harsh%20ji%20for%20this%20small%20but%20very%20powerful%20video.%20Bharat%20mata%20ki%20jai.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20fourth%20reasoned%20saying%2C%20''So%20American%20Corporate%20Greed%20is%20now%20India's%20counter%20policy%20against%20China%3F%20If%20India%20has%20IITs%2C%20then%20China%20also%20has%20Tsinghua%20and%20Peking.%20Think%20about%20it.''%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706164380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F2qgf1kv8_patrick-bet-david_625x300_25_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fvideo-us-podcaster-praises-indias-policies-says-country-not-afraid-of-china-4928419%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20short%20clip%20of%20the%20US%20author's%20podcast%20has%20gone%20viral%20after%20industrialist%20Harsh%20Goenka%20shared%20it%20on%20X.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fvideo-us-podcaster-praises-indias-policies-says-country-not-afraid-of-china-4928419%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fvideo-us-podcaster-praises-indias-policies-says-country-not-afraid-of-china-4928419%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fvideo-us-podcaster-praises-indias-policies-says-country-not-afraid-of-china-4928419%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Samsung%20Galaxy%20S24%20comes%20to%20Blinkit%2C%20promises%20delivery%20in%20minutes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706164031000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107135379%2Cimgsize-23394.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fsamsung-galaxy-s24-series-comes-to-blinkit-promises-delivery-in-minutes-in-these-cities%2Farticleshow%2F107135415.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Samsung%20partners%20with%20Blinkit%2C%20a%20Zomato-owned%20quick-commerce%20platform%2C%20to%20deliver%20Galaxy%20S24%20series%20smartphones%20in%20India%20in%20under%2010%20minutes.%20Customers%20in%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20Mumbai%20can%20order%20and%20receive%20the%20smartphones%20within%2010%20minutes.%20Additionally%2C%20customers%20purchasing%20through%20HDFC%20Bank%20credit%20card%20can%20avail%20an%20instant%20cashback%20of%20Rs%205%2C000.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fsamsung-galaxy-s24-series-comes-to-blinkit-promises-delivery-in-minutes-in-these-cities%2Farticleshow%2F107135415.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Admin%2C%20Infrastructure%2C%20Operational%20Woes%20Mount%20as%20JU%20Completes%20Month%208%20Without%20a%20Permanent%20V-C%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F14164408%2Fjadav-copy.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EKolkata%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20For%20over%20seven%20months%20now%2C%20Jadavpur%20University%2C%20one%20of%20the%20premier%20educational%20institutions%20in%20India%2C%20has%20been%20in%20a%20state%20of%20flux%20due%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20permanent%20vice-chancellor.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20last%20permanent%20vice-chancellor%2C%20Suranjan%20Das%2C%20retired%20after%20his%20nine-year%20stint%20on%20May%2031%2C%202023.%20West%20Bengal%20Governor%20C.V.%20Ananda%20Bose%2C%20the%20chancellor%20of%20state%20universities%2C%20did%20not%20extend%20his%20tenure.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20university%20has%20had%20two%20officiating%20V-Cs%2C%20both%20appointed%20and%20then%20dismissed%20by%20the%20Governor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOfficiating%20V-C%20Buddhadeb%20Sau%20was%20appointed%20by%20Raj%20Bhavan%20on%20August%2017%20last%20year.%20However%2C%20Governor%20Bose%20removed%20him%20on%20disciplinary%20grounds%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20annual%20convocation%20on%20December%2023%20last%20year.%20The%20state%20education%20department%2C%20at%20perpetual%20loggerheads%20with%20the%20governor%2C%20reinstated%20Sau%20the%20following%20day%2C%20but%20the%20convocation%20took%20place%20without%20the%20Chancellor%20%E2%80%93%20Governor%20Bose.%20Since%20then%2C%20Sau%20has%20been%20on%20leave%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20suspension%20of%20critical%20academic%20and%20administrative%20matters%20at%20the%20institution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20was%20posted%20on%20X%20by%20Bengal%20education%20minister%20Bratya%20Basu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22zxx%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FVm36jMwQrc%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FVm36jMwQrc%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Bratya%20Basu%20(%40basu_bratya)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbasu_bratya%2Fstatus%2F1738584598937006264%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2023%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20problems%20created%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20permanent%20V-C%20is%20that%20the%20working%20committee%20and%20executive%20council%20could%20not%20meet%20for%20months.%20Signing%20off%20on%20grants%20and%20approvals%20for%20crucial%20research%20work%20are%20also%20stalled.%20Recently%2C%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20teachers%E2%80%99%20association%20held%20a%20sit-in%20demonstration%20as%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Save%20JU%E2%80%99%20campaign.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFinancial%20transactions%20are%20on%20hold%20without%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20vice-chancellor%2C%20putting%20payments%20to%20temporary%20staff%20in%20jeopardy.%20The%20budget%20of%20the%20university%20could%20not%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20state%20government%20this%20time.%20The%20government%20did%20not%20allow%20a%20council%20meeting.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20there%20will%20be%20more%20serious%20problems%20in%20the%20future.%20In%20the%20face%20of%20this%20impasse%2C%20one%20section%20of%20officials%20are%20illegally%20giving%20work%20orders%20to%20their%20preferred%20organisations.%20These%20irregularities%20will%20continue%20until%20a%20permanent%20vice-chancellor%20takes%20charge%2C%E2%80%9D%20alleged%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPartha%20Pratim%20Roy%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Jadavpur%20University%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20Association%20(JUTA).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGovernor%20Bose%E2%80%99s%20controversial%20decision%20to%20appoint%20interim%20V-Cs%20in%2031%20state%20universities%2C%20including%20Jadavpur%20and%20Calcutta%20University%2C%20without%20consulting%20the%20higher%20education%20department%2C%20has%20triggered%20a%20seemingly%20unending%20conflict%20between%20the%20two%20and%20left%20these%20universities%20without%20permanent%20V-Cs.%20The%20state%20has%20challenged%20this%20move%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20further%20delay%20in%20the%20appointment%20of%20permanent%20V-Cs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20state-aided%20universities%20in%20West%20Bengal%20are%20under%20scrutiny%20for%20using%20their%20funds%20to%20defend%20Governor%20Bose%20in%20the%20legal%20battle%20with%20the%20state%20government%20over%20V-C%20appointments.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3ET%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fmy-kolkata%2Fnews%2Fvarsities-legal-expenses-for-bengal-governor-c-v-ananda-bose-to-be-probed%2Fcid%2F1991589%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3Ehe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Calcutta%20University%20and%20Jadavpur%20University%20have%20reportedly%20spent%20over%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20and%20Rs%2060%2C000%20respectively%20on%20legal%20matters%2C%20as%20confirmed%20by%20university%20officials.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20revelation%20has%20prompted%20the%20higher%20education%20department%20to%20set%20up%20a%20committee%20to%20investigate%20the%20%E2%80%9Cjustification%20of%20legal%20expenditure%E2%80%9D%20by%20these%20institutions.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20a%20search%20committee%20to%20be%20formed%20and%20a%20renowned%20academician%20to%20be%20appointed%20as%20V-C.%20The%20future%20of%20students%20is%20in%20question%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20between%20the%20state%20and%20the%20governor.%20The%20governor%20has%20termed%20the%20convocation%20as%20illegal.%20Now%2C%20if%20he%20cancels%20the%20certificates%20signed%20by%20the%20last%20interim%20V-C%20Buddhadeb%20Sau%2C%20we%20will%20be%20in%20trouble.%20The%20state%20government%20is%20strangely%20maintaining%20silence%20on%20the%20impasse%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Afreen%2C%20a%20student%20of%20the%20University.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEchoing%20Afreen%E2%80%99s%20concern%2C%20Anustup%20Chakraborty%2C%20a%20PhD%20student%2C%20said%20several%20other%20services%20were%20held%20up.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20absence%20of%20a%20permanent%20V-C%20is%20causing%20administrative%20problems%20for%20researchers%20and%20students.%20The%20allocation%20of%20research%20funds%20is%20stuck.%20The%20hostels%20are%20not%20being%20repaired.%20The%20infrastructure%20is%20crumbling.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20no%20secret%20that%20the%20university%20is%20facing%20severe%20financial%20distress.%20It%20has%20only%20a%20third%20of%20the%20funds%20it%20needs%20from%20the%20state.%20Thus%20maintaining%20infrastructure%2C%20providing%20adequate%20resources%2C%20and%20even%20basic%20functionality%20is%20hanging%20by%20a%20thread.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20suspension%20of%20student%20elections%20in%20recent%20years%20has%20also%20posed%20operational%20challenges%20for%20the%20campus%20anti-ragging%20cell%2C%20which%20comprises%20the%20V-C%20and%20elected%20student%20representatives.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20August%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjadavpur-university-ragging-death-swapnadeep-kundu%5C%22%3Ea%20student%E2%80%99s%20unnatural%20death%20in%20the%20university%20hostel%2C%20allegedly%20due%20to%20ragging%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20had%20sent%20shockwaves%20across%20the%20state.%20Twelve%20current%20and%20former%20students%20of%20the%20university%20are%20currently%20in%20judicial%20custody%20in%20the%20charge%20of%20abetment%20to%20suicide%20of%20a%20minor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20all%20the%20fuss%20about%20ragging%2C%20which%20damaged%20the%20reputation%20of%20the%20university%2C%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20students%3F%20Can%20only%20CCTV%20solve%20the%20problem%20if%20there%20is%20one%20to%20lead%20the%20university%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Rupam%20Basu%2C%20a%20student%20of%20the%20university.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Bengali%20original%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706163581000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F14164408%2Fjadav-copy.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fjadavpur-university-vice-chancellor-governor-cv-ananda-bose%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'The%20future%20of%20students%20is%20in%20question%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20between%20the%20state%20and%20the%20governor.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fjadavpu