%20cleaner%20walked%20in%20on%20them%20while%20they%20were%20naked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20of%20us%20were%20on%20the%20bed%20without%20our%20clothes%2C%20then%20we%20heard%20a%20sound%20at%20the%20door.%20And%20suddenly%20the%20door%20was%20opened%20before%20we%20could%20react%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20man%20who%20complained%2C%20identified%20only%20by%20his%20surname%20Huang%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gdtv.cn%2Ftv%2F900fc4ba87d58196c2972fd9ff5f9942%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprovincial%20TV%20station%20Guangdong%20Radio%20and%20TV.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20and%20his%20girlfriend%20were%20staying%20at%20the%20Ranz%20Hotel%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Shenzhen%20on%20Saturday%20and%20had%20arranged%20for%20a%20late%20checkout%20at%206%20p.m.%2C%20per%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20cleaner%20entered%20their%20room%20just%20after%205%20p.m.%2C%20and%20had%20failed%20to%20knock%2C%20Huang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20open%20at%20a%2090-degree%20angle%2C%20and%20because%20the%20room%20is%20small%2C%20the%20bed%20can%20be%20seen%20once%20you%20open%20the%20door%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Guangdong%20Radio%20and%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outlet%20reported%20that%20the%20cleaner%2C%20who%20was%20not%20named%2C%20said%20she%20assumed%20the%20guests%20had%20already%20checked%20out%20because%20it%20was%20late%20in%20the%20day%20and%20their%20room's%20lights%20appeared%20to%20be%20turned%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20front%20desk%20staff%20member%20at%20the%20Ranz%20Hotel%20confirmed%20the%20incident%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnew.qq.com%2Frain%2Fa%2F20240123A07H5500%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHunan-based%20daily%20Xiaoxiang%20Morning%20News.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20hotel%20disputed%20Huang's%20claim%20that%20the%20door%20was%20opened%20fully%2C%20saying%20surveillance%20footage%20from%20the%20hall%20showed%20the%20door%20was%20only%20opened%20at%20a%20small%20angle%20before%20the%20cleaner%20closed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20is%20now%20blaming%20the%20hotel%20for%20the%20mishap%20and%20has%20asked%20for%20compensation%20worth%2010%20times%20the%20cost%20of%20his%20stay%2C%20which%20was%20188%20yuan%2C%20or%20%2426.55%2C%20per%20Guangdong%20Radio%20and%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hotel%20told%20the%20outlet%20it%20could%20offer%20an%20apology%2C%20but%20not%20the%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%2010%20times%20the%20room%20rate%2C%20that's%20an%20impossibility%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lobby%20manager%2C%20identified%20by%20his%20surname%20as%20Xie%2C%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fregional.chinadaily.com.cn%2Fpdf%2FCivilCodeofthePeople%2527sRepublicofChina.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecivil%20code%3C%2Fa%3E%20states%20that%20hotel%20operators%20bear%20responsibility%20if%20they%20%26quot%3Bfail%20to%20fulfill%20the%20duty%20of%20maintaining%20safety%26quot%3B%20of%20their%20guests%2C%20but%20does%20not%20specifically%20mention%20guests'%20privacy%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang's%20complaint%20went%20viral%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F2054900587%2FNDc16azZw%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E230%20million%20views%20on%20Weibo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20China's%20version%20of%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ranz%20Hotel%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20by%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-couple-caught-naked-hotel-room-demand-10-times-rate-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706158182000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b1d6da43bb77284ba0725c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-couple-caught-naked-hotel-room-demand-10-times-rate-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ho