agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Ottawa%20went%20public%2C%20a%20political%20ally%2C%20New%20Democratic%20Party%20leader%20Jagmeet%20Singh%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FtheJagmeetSingh%2Fstatus%2F1704217846732222483%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Ewritten%20to%20the%20Commission%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20look%20into%20India%20having%20influenced%20elections%20through%20its%20large%20diaspora%2C%20just%20like%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20vehemently%20denied%20the%20accusation%2C%20with%20both%20countries%20expelling%20a%20diplomat%20each.%20India%20had%20also%20stopped%20visa%20services%20for%20Canadian%20nationals%2C%20which%20it%20resumed%20after%20about%20a%20month.%20New%20Delhi%20also%20asked%20Canada%20to%20cut%20down%20its%20diplomatic%20presence%20so%20that%20there%20is%20parity%2C%20which%20led%20Ottawa%20to%20withdraw%20over%2040%20diplomats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20relations%20with%20Canada%20continued%20to%20be%20in%20the%20freezer%2C%20US%20federal%20prosecutors%20announced%20in%20November%20that%20there%20was%20a%20possible%20link%20between%20the%20killing%20of%20Nijjar%20and%20the%20foiling%20of%20a%20plant%20to%20kill%20a%20Canadian%20American%20Khalistani%20supporter%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fpannun-assassination-plot-india-enquiry-committee-set-up%5C%22%3EAn%20unsealed%20indictment%3C%2Fa%3E%20accused%20an%20Indian%20national%2C%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20currently%20in%20Czech%20custody%2C%20of%20attempting%20to%20hire%20a%20hitman%20to%20kill%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannu%2C%20a%20lawyer%20for%20Sikhs%20for%20Justice%2C%20a%20group%20banned%20by%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20charges%2C%20Gupta%20was%20allegedly%20told%20to%20hire%20the%20hitman%2C%20who%20was%20an%20undercover%20operative%2C%20on%20the%20instructions%20of%20an%20Indian%20government%20agent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20Commission%20will%20release%20an%20interim%20report