0an%20alliance%20and%20there%20will%20be%20cooperation%20among%20all%20the%20parties.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamesh%E2%80%99s%20statement%20came%20hours%20after%20Banerjee%20told%20reporters%20that%20she%20will%20go%20it%20alone%20at%20least%20in%20Bengal%20and%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20will%20be%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20given%20them%20a%20proposal%20and%20they%20had%20turned%20it%20down.%20Since%20then%20we%20had%20decided%20that%20we%20will%20go%20it%20alone%20in%20Bengal%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20which%20will%20enter%20West%20Bengal%20through%20Cooch%20Behar%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Banerjee%20said%20that%20she%20had%20not%20been%20informed%20about%20the%20yatra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20doing%20a%20yatra%2C%20but%20have%20they%20even%20informed%20me%20even%20once%20that%20we%20are%20coming%20to%20your%20state%3F%20No%20they%20have%20not.%20Hence%20I%20have%20no%20communication%20with%20them%20about%20Bengal.%20We%20will%20think%20about%20what%20to%20do%20or%20not%20to%20do%20on%20an%20all-India%20level%2C%20we%20are%20a%20secular%20party%20and%20we%20will%20do%20everything%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamesh%20said%20during%20his%20press%20conference%20that%20the%20Congress%20had%20already%20invited%20all%20INDIA%20alliance%20partners%20to%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKharge%20(Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge)%20has%20already%20spoken%2C%20Rahulji%20has%20also%20spoken%20about%20it.%20If%20there%20was%20a%20written%20invitation%20I%20will%20check%20and%20let%20you%20know.%20But%20I%20know%20that%20Khargeji%20has%20already%20said%20at%20least%20three%20or%20four%20times%20in%20his%20speeches%20that%20we%20are%20inviting%20all%20INDIA%20alliance%20partners%20and%20he%20has%20spoken%20to%20every%20alliance%20partner.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20in%