%20knew%20their%20target%20quite%20well.%20Shops%20sporting%20saffron%20flags%20with%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%20printed%20on%20them%20had%20to%20be%20spared%2C%20the%20rest%20were%20all%20to%20be%20attacked.%20Saba%20Boutique%20was%20one%20such%20establishment%20owned%20by%20Muslims%20among%20the%20otherwise%20Hindu-dominated%20shopping%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20passing%20commotion%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shamsher%20Alam%2C%20owner%20of%20the%2013-year-old%20boutique%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20men%2C%20most%20of%20them%20in%20their%20teens%20and%2020s%2C%20barged%20into%20the%20boutique%20and%20pelted%20stones.%20Almost%20all%20of%20them%20had%20backpacks%20and%20appeared%20to%20have%20stored%20big%20stones%20in%20them.%20They%20hurled%20stones%20at%20the%20shop%2C%20destroyed%20glass%20panes%20and%20mannequins%20placed%20outside%20the%20boutique%20and%20moved%20ahead.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20all%20over%20within%2030%20seconds%2C%E2%80%9D%20Alam%20added.%20His%20son%20and%20brother-in-law%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F24210428%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-24-at-20.50.22.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F24210428%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-24-at-20.50.22.jpeg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F24210428%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-24-at-20.50.22-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F24210428%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-24-at-20.50.22-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694309%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESaba%20Boutique%2C%20one%20of%20the%20many%20shops%20owned%20by%20Muslims%20that%20was%20destroyed%20in%20the%20attack.%20Photo%3A%20Sukanya%20Shantha.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crowd%20had%20then%20moved%20to%20other%20shop%20establishments%20belonging%20to%20Muslims%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20lane.%20Even%20as%20the%20attack%20continued%2C%20the%20local%20police%20from%20the%20Naya%20Nagar%20police%20station%20were%20seen%20standing%20on%20the%20street%2C%20just%2020%20metres%20away.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20the%20mob.%20It%20was%20almost%20as%20if%20the%20police%20were%20there%20for%20the%20mob%E2%80%99s%20safety%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20January%2024%2C%20Alam%20and%20other%20shop%20owners%20who%20incurred%20massive%20losses%20in%20the%20attack%20had%20visited%20the%20police%20station.%20The%20police%2C%20they%20claimed%2C%20refused%20to%20file%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20despite%20producing%20damning%20evidence.%20In%20many%20other%20shops%20that%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20visited%2C%20shop%20owners%20had%20identical%20stories%20to%20narrate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShaikh%20Faiyyaz%20Ahmed%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20Chote%20Nawab%20shoe%20shop%20showed%20CCTV%20footage%20of%20the%20time%20when%20his%20shop%20was%20attacked.%20Young%20boys%2C%20most%20likely%20in%20their%20teens%2C%20could%20be%20seen%20pelting%20stones%20at%20the%20shop.%20They%20too%20had%20heavy%20backpacks%2C%20filled%20with%20stones.%20Some%20had%20their%20faces%20covered%2C%20many%20didn%E2%80%99t%20care%20to%20cover%20their%20faces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20sector%203%2C%20a%20tempo%20driver%20was%20attacked%20by%20the%20mob.%20His%20tempo%20had%20%E2%80%9CRashid%20Tempo%20Service%E2%80%9D%20painted%20on%20the%20back.%2021-year-old%20Mohammad%20Tariq%20and%20two%20others%20were%20injured%20in%20this%20attack.%20At%20a%20mobile%20shop%20close%20by%20another%2049-year-old%20man%20was%20injured%20in%20the%20attack.%20Mohammad%20Umar%2C%20originally%20from%20Gujarat%2C%20works%20at%20a%20local%20optician.%20The%20shop%2C%20although%20had%20a%20neutral-sounding%20name%20%E2%80%98Blue%20Eye%E2%80%99%2C%20was%20still%20attacked.%20That%20Umar%20says%20happened%20for%20two%20reasons.%20One%2C%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20saffron%20flag%20outside%20the%20shop%20and%20two%2C%20the%20men%20with%20their%20beards%20%E2%80%9Clooked%20Muslim%E2%80%9D.%20The%20apprehension%20of%20being%20attacked%20for%20not%20sporting%20a%20saffron%20flag%20makes%20sense%20as%20another%20optical%20shop%20Gangar%20Eyenation%20was%20attacked%20too.%20The%20shop%2C%20owned%20by%20a%20Hindu%20person%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20saffron%20flag%20hoisted%20outside%20the%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Sachin%20Salvi%20appearing%20for%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20attack%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Eafter%20persuing%20the%20police%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20they%20finally%20filed%20FIR%20in%20four%20cases.%20One%20of%20them%20was%20against%20a%20mob%20that%20attacked%20a%2016-year-old%20boy%20who%20was%20attacked%20on%20the%20road.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20boy%20had%20to%20be%20hospitalised%20after%20the%20attack.%20The%20police%20were%20reluctant%20to%20file%20FIRs%20but%20when%20we%20refused%20to%20budge%2C%20they%20finally%20took%20the%20FIR%2C%E2%80%9D%20Salvi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJanuary%2023%20was%20day%203%20of%20the%20violence%20that%20broke%20out%20in%20Mira%20Road%2C%20a%20fast-%20developing%20neighbourhood%20in%20Thane%20district.%20According%20to%20the%202011%20census%20data%2C%20Mira%20Road%20has%20over%2016%25%20Muslim%20population.%20In%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20as%20the%20population%20of%20Mumbai%20began%20to%20burst%20at%20the%20seams%2C%20people%20had%20to%20move%20to%20faraway%20suburban%20areas%20like%20Mira%20Road%20and%20Bhayander.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20region%20still%20has%20a%20sizeable%20free%20land%20parcel%20and%20many%20real%20estate%20developers%20have%20been%20eyeing%20the%20region.%20Many%20Muslim%20locals%20who%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20drew%20a%20connection%20between%20the%20attack%20and%20the%20booming%20real%20estate%20business%20in%20the%20area.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20always%20easier%20to%20attract%20buyers%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20as%20many%20Muslims%20in%20the%20area.%20That%20way%20the%20property%20sounds%20more%20cosmopolitan%20and%20real%20estate%20prices%20shoot%20up%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mohammad%20Khalid%20Siddiqui%2C%20a%20local%20social%20activist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJanuary%2022%20incident%20was%20not%20out%20of%20some%20sudden%20provocation.%20Locals%20say%20it%20was%20well-planned.%20The%20police%20were%20in%20fact%20patrolling%20major%20roads%20of%20the%20city.%20But%20they%20failed%20to%20stop%20attacks.%20Just%20an%20hour%20before%20the%20attack%2C%20the%20Mira%20Bhayander%20municipal%20corporation%20decided%20to%20raze%20several%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20structures%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20ground.%20At%20Haidary%20Chowk%20in%20the%20Naya%20Nagar%20area%20of%20Mir%20Road%2C%20seven%20kutcha%20structures%20were%20flattened%20by%20the%20corporation%20bull%20dozers.%20These%20structures%20have%20existed%20in%20the%20area%20for%20more%20than%20two%20decades.%20But%20not%20once%20have%20the%20people%20running%20them%20received%20a%20notice%20or%20prior%20warning%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShamim%20Ahmed%2C%20who%20ran%20a%20workshop%20of%20two-wheeler%20vehicles%20from%20one%20of%20the%20tin-structures%20for%20over%2010%20years%20said%20at%20around%205%20pm%20some%20officials%20of%20the%20local%20corporation%E2%80%94backed%20by%20a%20large%20team%20of%20local%20police%20and%20Rapid%20Action%20Force%20(RAF)%E2%80%94landed%20at%20their%20shops.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20physically%20pulled%20us%20out%20and%20began%20demolition%20of%20the%20structures%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ahmed%20said.%20Those%20who%20lost%20their%20shops%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20attacks%20that%20occurred%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20Mira%20Road.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20became%20easy%20targets%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20incident%20occurred%20on%20January%2021.%20It%20was%20around%2010%3A30%20pm%2C%20when%20several%20young%20men%20entered%20Banegar%20galli%20in%20Naya%20Nagar.%20Almost%20all%20houses%20in%20this%20area%20belongs%20to%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20The%20men%2C%20locals%20claim%2C%20were%20blaring%20loud%20music%20and%20chanting%20%E2%80%9CJai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%9D.%20They%20finally%20stopped%20outside%20Sanghvi%20Empire%20housing%20society%20and%20played%20loud%20music.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20building%20is%20at%20the%20dead%20end%20of%20the%20road.%20The%20men%20knew%20there%20was%20no%20other%20route%20to%20get%20out%20from%20there.%20They%20were%20not%20passing%20by%20but%20had%20come%20with%20an%20intention%20to%20provoke%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Zuleikha%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Singhvi%20Empire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Muslim%20locals%20entered%20into%20a%20heated%20argument%20with%20the%20Hindutva%20men%20and%20the%20argument%20soon%20got%20violent.%20Videos%20have%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20and%20local%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20used%20it%20to%20flare-up%20communal%20sentiments%20in%20the%20state.%20Soon%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20Maharashtra%20deputy%20minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20had%20announced%20that%20%E2%80%9Cstrict%20action%E2%80%9D%20would%20be%20taken%20against%20anybody%20trying%20to%20disturb%20law%20and%20order%20in%20the%20state.%2013%20men%20were%20arrested%20soon%20after.%20Of%20them%2C%20two%20are%20Zuleikha%E2%80%99s%20sons.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20police%20took%20away%20our%20children.%20But%20did%20not%20question%20the%20men%20who%20had%20entered%20the%20area%20and%20were%20shouting%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%20slogans%20late%20at%20night%E2%80%9D%2C%20she%20complained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20arrested%2C%20two%20are%20minors%20and%20have%20been%20sent%20to%20a%20children%E2%80%99s%20home%20in%20Bhiwandi.%20A%20few%20more%20arrests%20were%20made%20on%20January%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20filed%20another%20FIR%20against%20a%20man%20named%20Abu%20Shama%20who%20allegedly%20recorded%20a%20video%20of%20himself%20lamenting%20the%20state%20of%20affairs%20in%20the%20country%20and%20blaming%20the%20local%20politicians%20for%20fanning%20communal%20hatred%20in%20the%20country.%20Shama%20was%20arrested%20today%20(January%2024).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20said%20that%20action%20is%20being%20taken%20against%20anybody%20posting%20provocative%20messages%20and%20videos%20on%20social%20media.%20However%2C%20no%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20against%20BJP%20MLA%20Geeta%20Jain%20or%20BJP%20leader%20Nitish%20Rane%2C%20who%20have%20openly%20made%20provocative%20statements%20and%20threatened%20the%20Muslim%20community%20with%20dire%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%A1%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AF%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B2%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%9D%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B2..%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%95%20%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A6%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%96%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE..%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E0%A4%9A%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%9A%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%97%E0%A5%87%20!!!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%AF%20%E0%A4%B6%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AE%20%F0%9F%9A%A9%F0%9F%9A%A9%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20nitesh%20rane%20(%40NiteshNRane)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNiteshNRane%2Fstatus%2F1749286752815399328%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3