0w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FBamboo-3-1-1706104420-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FBamboo-3-1-1706104420-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-339673%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJohnson%20has%20collected%20bamboo%20species%20from%20across%20the%20country%20including%20Nagaland%2C%20Manipur%2C%20Sikkim%2C%20Arunachal%2C%20and%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20decades%2C%20the%20residents%20along%20the%20Kerala-Karnataka%20border%20of%20Wayanad%20district%2C%20especially%20in%20villages%20on%20the%20northeastern%20tip%20of%20the%20Deccan%20Plateau%20including%20Pulpally%2C%20Mullankolly%2C%20and%20Poothadi%20have%20been%20facing%20desertification%20owing%20to%20a%20sharp%20decline%20in%20rainfall%2C%20loss%20of%20organic%20matter%20in%20soil%2C%20unscientific%20land%20use%2C%20conversion%20of%20wetlands%20and%20shortage%20in%20the%20canopy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohnson%20believes%20farming%20with%20Bamboo%20could%20be%20an%20ideal%20and%20effective%20method%20for%20a%20sustainable%20model%20to%20check%20the%20desertification%20tendencies%20of%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBamboo%20is%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20growing%20plant%20species.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20low-cost%20method%20to%20absorb%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20carbon.%20It%20produces%20about%2035%20percent%20more%20oxygen%20than%20any%20other%20plant%20creating%20an%20oxygen%20park%20in%20nature%20for%20future%20generations.%20It%20can%20boost%20the%20moisture%20content%20and%20the%20organic%20carbon%20in%20the%20soil%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20mentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20its%20low-cost%20carbon%20sequestration%20property%2C%20Johnson%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBamboo%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20next%20timber%20in%20the%20world%20because%20of%20it