a%2C%20whatever%20that%20is%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20supposed%20to%20be%20myself%20two%20times%20over%3F%20Makes%20me%20sound%20like%20I%E2%80%99ve%20got%20a%20split%20personality.%20How%20did%20all%20this%20come%20about%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakshman%3A%20It%E2%80%99s%20all%20part%20and%20parcel%20of%20the%20change%20in%20how%20the%20calendar%20is%20now%20divided.%20Previously%2C%20everything%20was%20dated%20BCE%2C%20Before%20Common%20Era%2C%20and%20CE%2C%20Common%20Era.%20Now%20everything%20is%20divided%20into%20PM%20or%20PM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERam%3A%20But%20PM%20and%20PM%20are%20one%20and%20the%20same!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakshman%3A%20They%20are%2C%20and%20they%20aren%E2%80%99t.%20One%20PM%20is%20for%20Pre%20Mandir%20and%20the%20other%20is%20for%20Post%20Mandir.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20great%20watershed%20dividing%20everything%20and%20everyone.%20Including%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERam%3A%20I%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20videos%20of%20this%20mandir%20on%20YouTube%2C%20and%20very%20snazzy%20it%20is%20too.%20But%20why%20should%20it%20be%20such%20a%20dividing%20factor%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakshman%3A%20Because%20having%20built%20it%2C%20the%20government%20has%20put%20its%20own%20stamp%20on%20it.%20And%2C%20by%20extension%2C%20its%20stamp%20on%20you.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20Opposition%20claims%20you%20as%20its%20own.%20So%20there%20are%20two%20yous%3A%20a%20government%20you%20and%20an%20Opposition%20you.%20A%20double%20role%2C%20so%20to%20speak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERam%3A%20Hey%20Ram!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakshman%3A%20The%20two%20yous%20can%20say%20that%20again%2C%20twice%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJug%20Suraiya%20is%20a%20columnist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706096983000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F24171634%2Fmodi-ram-modi-print.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhumour%2Fram-redoubled-forget-bce-and-ce-eras-will-now-divided-int