20four.%20Playing%20for%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20state%20team%20at%20just%20eight%20years%20old%2C%20she%20was%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20under-19%20state%20team.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20sights%20set%20on%20joining%20the%20national%20team%20along%20with%20achieving%20excellence%20in%20academics%2C%20she%20felt%20that%20everything%20was%20going%20her%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20even%20the%20shadow%20of%20failure%20had%20touched%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20everything%20changed%20in%20the%20blink%20of%20an%20eye%20when%20she%20was%2018.%20Enjoying%20with%20her%20friends%20on%20a%20Puducherry%20beach%2C%20she%20suddenly%20fell%20down%20while%20playing%20in%20the%20water.%20A%20spinal%20cord%20injury%20left%20her%20without%20any%20feeling%20under%20the%20neck.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20unwavering%20love%20and%20support%20of%20her%20parents%2C%20and%20her%20incredible%20resilience%2C%20she%20emerged%20like%20a%20phoenix%2C%20and%20today%20provides%20wings%20to%20hundreds%20of%20people%20with%20spinal%20cord%20injury%20through%20her%20venture%20%E2%80%98Soulfree%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20charitable%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoulfree%20INSPIRE%20(Integrated%20Spinal%20Rehabilitation%20Centre)%20in%202013%2C%20the%20trust%E2%80%99s%20rehab%20centre%2C%20provides%20holistic%20treatment%2C%20rehabilitation%2C%20medical%20care%2C%20education%2C%20counselling%2C%20employment%20opportunities%20to%20persons%20with%20spinal%20cord%20injuries%20for%20free.%20The%2020%2C000%20square%20feet%20facility%20in%20Tiruvannamalai%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20has%20helped%20over%20200%20people%20with%20severe%20disabilities%20live%20a%20life%20of%20dignity%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESwimming%20against%20the%20tide%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201074px)%20100vw%2C%201074px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A