be%20afraid%20to%20do%20something%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20part%20of%20the%20problem.%20No%20one%20understands%20this%20better%20than%20me%20due%20to%20my%20lived%20experience.%20I%20decided%20to%20raise%20my%20voice%20and%20do%20whatever%20I%20can%20to%20somehow%20uplift%20this%20segment%20of%20society%20because%20we%E2%80%99re%20so%20completely%20invisible%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20in%20mind%2C%20she%20started%20Soulfree%20Inspire.%20People%20come%20with%20a%20caregiver%20and%20spend%20about%206%20months%20in%20the%20centre.%20They%20receive%20training%2C%20which%20Preethi%20calls%20re-engineering%2C%20where%20they%20get%20emotional%20and%20physical%20rehabilitation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20restore%20their%20will%20to%20live.%20Our%20aim%20is%20to%20restore%20self-reliance%20from%20a%20physiological%2C%20psychological%20and%20socio%20economic%20perspective.%20It%E2%80%99s%20important%20for%20them%20to%20go%20home%20and%20be%20able%20to%20earn%20some%20money.%20We%20are%20giving%20international%20standards%20of%20care%20free%20of%20cost.%20We%20have%20physiotherapy%2C%20occupational%20therapy%2C%20hydrotherapy%2C%20sports%2C%20counselling%20sessions%2C%20training%20sessions%2C%20tailoring%2C%20computer%20classes%20and%20more.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20holistic%20system%20born%20from%20an%20experiential%20framework%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Preethi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoulfree%20also%20offers%20knowledge%20and%20awareness%20programs%20about%20spinal%20cord%20injury.%20They%20have%20a%20special%20focus%20on%20women%20and%20provide%20a%20support%20system%20to%20those%20with%20severe%20disabilities%20through%20educational%20and%20employment%20opportunities.%20They%20also%20provide%20wheelchairs%20and%20medical%20care%20to%20those%20in%20need.%20To%20keep%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20spirits%20up%2C%20they%20also%20have%20conference%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarthikeyan%20(25)%2C%20was%20bedridden%20after%20he%20fell%20from%20a%20tree%20t