n%20different%20tasks%20like%20hospitality%2C%20housekeeping%20and%20trek%20guiding%20and%20given%20them%20jobs%20at%20the%20homestay%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAdventure%2C%20nature%20and%20culture%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20initial%20response%20of%20the%20tourists%2C%20Bishar%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20back%20in%202014%2C%20while%20it%20was%20a%20good%20dream%2C%20the%20initial%20response%20was%20not%20how%20we%20expected%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Ftravellers-nest-1705668981.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20activities%20at%20the%20homestay%20are%20divided%20into%20two%20categories%20based%20in%20seasons.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Ftravellers-nest-1705668981.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Ftravellers-nest-1705668981-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Ftravellers-nest-1705668981-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Ftravellers-nest-1705668981-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Ftravellers-nest-1705668981-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-338642%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20activities%20at%20the%20homestay%20are%20divided%20into%20two%20categories%20based%20on%20seasons.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Bishar%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20exciting%20things%20that%20the%20place%20had%20to%20offer%2C%20a%20lack%20of%20awareness%20prevailed.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20via%20Facebook%20and%20Google%20search%20that%20a%20few%20people%20started%20to%20visit%20us.%20With%20word%20of%20mouth%2C%20we%20started%20getting%20more%20and%20more%20visitors%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20hosted%20nearly%20300%20people%20this%20year%20alone.%20The%20popularity%20has%20increased%20and%20we%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20inquiries%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20various%20activities%20that%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337937%2Fbest-budget-homestay-in-uttarakhand-the-nanda-stone-mukteshwar-by-ashish-verma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20the%20homestay%20%3C%2Fa%3Eoffers%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20few%20activities%20at%20our%20homestays.%20We%20have%20divided%20them%20according%20to%20the%20season%20%E2%80%94%20monsoons%20and%20winters.%20Most%20of%20them%20are%20related%20to%20water%20sports%20like%20Cliff%20Jumping%2C%20River%20Canyoning%2C%20Kayaking%2C%20etc.%20We%20also%20organise%20treks%20to%20explore%20the%20nearby%20areas%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20types%20of%20treks%20%E2%80%94%20short%20and%20long%20treks.%20%E2%80%9CA%20long%20trek%20is%20around%20four%20hours%20and%20a%20short%20trek%20is%20about%202%20hours%20long.%20On%20those%20treks%2C%20you%20can%20enjoy%20the%20landscapes%2C%20enjoy%20bathing%20in%204%20waterfalls%2C%20you%20can%20see%20the%20fossils%20and%20the%20magnificent%20rock%20formations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20homestay%20also%20arranges%20cave%20exploration%20for%20the%20guests%20on%20request.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20trained%20nearly%2040%20locals%20as%20trek%20guides%20to%20help%20people%20in%20these%20treks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20exploring%20the%20wilderness%2C%20the%20homestay%20also